A CITY Centre gin bar was closed after the building was deemed dangerous. Gin bar shuts at 'danger' city building A CITY Centre gin bar was closed after the building was deemed dangerous.Gin 71, on the corner of Renfield Street and West Regent Street, was shut and sealed off yesterday.A sign posted on a fence at the site said &quot;essential maintenance&quot; work had to be carried outPart of the road was sectioned off and motorists were warned of delays. 